N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15ยง 1.6 - Restrictions on class DJ and class MJ driver's licenses issued prior to january 1, 1990

State Regulations

Class DJ and MJ driver's license issued prior to January 1, 1990 shall be subject to the restrictions which were in effect on December 31, 1989. Notes
